                        <span class="section-desc fs-20">get acquainted with the basics of WEB programming, structure, modern approaches,</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row desc">
                    <div class="col-md-1 col-2 my-auto"><img src="~/image/icons/circle-check-yellow.png" class="img-fluid" alt="icon" /></div>
                    <div class="col-md-11 col-10">
                        <span class="section-desc fs-20">study and use the HTML language of web programming and its capabilities</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row desc">
                    <div class="col-md-1 col-2 my-auto"><img src="~/image/icons/circle-check-yellow.png" class="img-fluid" alt="icon" /></div>
